stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> awaiting_forge : dream creates proposal brief
    awaiting_forge --> awaiting_user : tool propose submit [requirements + tool.md + source + path lint pass]
    awaiting_forge --> awaiting_forge : tool propose submit [path lint fails]
    awaiting_user --> approved : tool propose approve
    awaiting_user --> rejected : tool propose reject
    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*] : rejection_count < 3
    rejected --> [*] : rejection_count = 3 (pattern blacklisted)

    note right of awaiting_user
        On submit: attach hardened
        requirement, tool.md, source, optional tests,
        dependencies, and correctness argument.
    end note

    note right of approved
        DB transaction:
        registry insert + reviewed tool.md
        + seed memory
        + proposal status flip.
        Binary install follows
        registry mutation protocol.
    end note

    note left of rejected
        Blacklist is enforced as a
        dream-side guard (count check
        before drafting), not as a state.
    end note
